						               													<description>a cooperative 3D Tower Defense game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Try and stop the conquistadors from entering and destroying the Bacab Temple. &amp;#10;Work together simultaneous as a team to manipulate the tower, upgrade the weapons and turn each section for maximum damage.&amp;#10;Survive the onslaught for 6 or 8 rounds to win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each round has 7 phases&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1. Building phase: &amp;#10;Build new weapons or abilities onto the tower&amp;#10;Research the next level of your abilities &amp;#10;Upgrade abilities on the tower to a next level&amp;#10;&amp;#10;2. Turning phase:&amp;#10;Pass resources to other players by putting resources on the top of the tower&amp;#10;Decide as a group which levels of the tower to turn. To give each player the best fighting chance to win the next attack.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;3.Second building phase:&amp;#10;Now the tower levels have turned, a new building opportunity has risen.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;4. Attack phase:&amp;#10;Everybody can now attack the conquistadors in front of him, using the damage and abilities on the tower.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;5. Resource phase:&amp;#10;Each player looks at the resource abilities on the tower on his side and multiply them by the same resource regions on his part of the battle map.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;6. Move conquistadors phase:&amp;#10;Move all the conquistadors that are still alive one space closer to the tower. If they would enter the tower the game is lost.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;7. Spawn phase:&amp;#10;Each player spawns 2 new conquistadors on his side of the board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
